PrecisAppointment of a temporary Administrator, namely Mr. Justice JEAN-CLAUDE ANGERS, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of New Brunswick, who shall execute the office and functions of the LIEUTENANT GOVERNOR of NEW BRUNSWICK over the course of a nine-day period in August, 1990 (August 23-31).
